ğŸ”§ Configuration
Main Config (config/config.yaml)
YAML

models:
  default_model: "yolov8s"
  available_models: ["yolov8n", "yolov8s", "yolov8m"]

data:
  classes: ["person", "car", "bicycle", ...]
  augmentation:
    enabled: true
    horizontal_flip: 0.5

training:
  batch_size: 16
  epochs: 100
  learning_rate: 0.001
Model-Specific Configs
config/model_configs/yolo_config.yaml
config/model_configs/rcnn_config.yaml
config/model_configs/ssd_config.yaml
ğŸ§ª Training Custom Models
Prepare Dataset
Bash

# Organize data in YOLO format
data/
â”œâ”€â”€ train/
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ images/
